---
title: Bibimbap-Style Rice Bowls and Spicy Sesame Sauce with Beyond Meat®, Zucchini and Carrots
description: Our take on the Korean rice bowl is packed with veggies, rice and Beyond Meat®. Finish it with a spicy-sweet sesame sauce, then stir all these vibrant ingredients together.
